<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
      /* Add some basic styling */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #004a99;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .button {
        background-color: #004a99;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Welcome, <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>!</h1>
      <p>Thank you for signing up for Chambers For Sport. We're excited to have you on board.</p>

      <p>To get started, please log in using the following link:</p>

      <p><a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Sign In</a></p>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The Chambers For Sport Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
